===Etymology===
From {{etyl|grc|en}} {{m|grc|πεῖ}}. Its mathematical use apparently stems from its use as the first letter in {{m|el|περιφέρεια||periphery; circumference}} and was first cited in 1706 in the ''Synopsis Palmariorum Matheseos'' by [[w:William Jones (mathematician)|William Jones]].

